    "description": "Defend against evil snails with a variety of plants. It's up to you to choose the best towers in each level and develope the ultimate tactic. Snails come with different stats and get stronger over time. <br>What makes this TD SPECIAL are the power-ups for enemies YOU have to choose.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115720/extras/a89fb5d3adf46b0915b7b2fdb8a8700c.poster.avif?t=1669828593\" width=614 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115720/extras/a89fb5d3adf46b0915b7b2fdb8a8700c.webm?t=1669828593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115720/extras/a89fb5d3adf46b0915b7b2fdb8a8700c.mp4?t=1669828593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build and upgrade plants!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Many unique plants:</strong> - You place fruits and vegetables all over the map finding the best positions for an effective defense. Combine their strengths to make them even stronger.<br></li><li><strong>Upgrade plants:</strong> - Upgrade plants to their max level of 5.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend against strong enemies!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Enemies are snails:</strong> - Fight against evil snails with different size, speed and health.<br></li><li><strong>Six special power-ups:</strong> - Every few waves you choose one out of three random power-ups for enemies.</li></ul>  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115720/extras/7f23d0c74b563834ef6585ccdc23836b.avif?t=1669828593\" width=600 height=216 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115720/extras/cb045b3d5cc4d3aa6e20f2a28e11d084.avif?t=1669828593\" width=600 height=214 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your tactical ability in different game modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Three different game modes:</strong> Destroy Crystals (easy/hard) and Endless Mode</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Diverse maps:</strong> Fight on maps with many different mechanics like teleport, blocking paths, power-ups and much more!</li></ul>",
